Keep your living clean and tidy with the Swivel Sweeper G6 Upgraded. With Quad Brush technology, this cordless swivel sweeper efficiently picks up dirt on all four sides. This unit is cordless. The dirt tray that comes with this cordless swivel sweeper easily collects and disposes off the dirt. The pole bends easily making cleaning hard-to-reach areas. For easy storage, the latch keeps the handle folded.

Super light weight 100% microfiber mop with super absorbent capacity. Mini Cleaning Sweeper Kitchen Dust Pan and Brush Set.This dust pan hand sweeper combination are a household essential.
